Qlik Cli Connection Problem in Qlik Sense Environment

Ive always used jwt authentication method when connecting to QS client managed (its easier at least) by following the getting started documentation When connecting to port 4747 (in general) you have to use some sort of authentication as well. The allowed methods in that case are certificates or jwt (since the token is generated from the certificates and can be verified by the engine). Although i havent tested direct engine connection myself with qlik-cli.
